casebody.data:
Judith K. BUCKNER and Mark A. Buckner, Plaintiffs-Appellees,
v.
GREAT SOUTHERN BANCORP, INC., d/b/a Great Southern Bank, a Missouri Corporation, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0473 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

In this interlocutory appeal, the defendants challenge the district court's denial of a pre-answer motion to dismiss the plaintiffs' personal-injury action for failure to serve process. REVERSED AND REMANDED.

REVERSED. REMANDED.
